name: Reconstruct #1: Armless
description: When I hit by quarter life crisis, I didn't know what to do and that moment, I was broke, unemployed but not jobless. So, feeling ungrateful was the result. I didn't tell anyone who close just swallow all the feelings by my self. Then, I found a way to release the stress by capturing any objects. So, I walked alone, without purpose and destination. Just walking and bringing camera in my hands. Difficult time, but I already passed it. These series of photo that I took when I walked down the street. I hope that we as human can embrace ourselves that we should live the life. Because we only live once.
